cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.IR

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and machine translation.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses an encoder-decoder architecture and multilingual sentence representations.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing a technique for low-resource scenarios.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the LASER toolkit has also been used for image captioning tasks.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with scoring and filtering parallel sentences.
